room_title: Escape room "The Pharaoh's Tomb" by The Escape Room in South Portland
room_description: You've arrived in Cairo to join an archaeological expedition. When you come to the dig site, you discover an ancient abandoned pharaoh's tomb. Locals believe the tomb to be cursed, and the previous team of researchers who descended into the darkness of the tomb were never seen again. Can you find the missing archaeologists in 60 minutes or will you succumb to the same fate?
